    title: 'POST-COMBAT',
    body: '''Groups revealed in combat are now returned to the map but remain face up and may be examined, along with their numeral markers, by other players at any time. If Groups start their turn in the same hex as one of their Colonies, they may be flipped face down (hiding their numeral marker also) before being moved (if able) and remain that way until they once again engage in combat.''',
